node.text: Here’s another recipe from #EvolvingVegan and it’s one of my favorites for the Fall. It’s a good one to have up your sleeve with the holidays coming up. node.text:
The feeling of holding my book #EvolvingVegan for the first time has been unreal. Seeing all the hard work and dedication come together to form these pages is something I’ll never forget. Take a watch for a sneak peek at some of the recipes and pre-order your copy now at the link in my bio.

@evolvingvegan @simonandschuster @simonschusterca

node.text: I’m turning 30 this year & I’ve been thinking. It’s time to get less precious about my posts & what I share with all my incredible fans. I’m going to be ramping up my social media because I think it’s important to go all in or not at all. More news coming soon, but to start here’s a random photo I took in Venice. Just out & about. Rarely anything is perfect so why the heck are we always pretending it is. Embrace this coming week & all it’s imperfections!

node.text: I’m laughing at how GOOD this burger is. I’m telling you guys, @motif_foodworks is changing the plant-based game! By reinventing food design rules and using innovative science, Motif ingredients are about to make #plantbased foods taste better, more nutritious and craveable. Check out the link in my bio for more on how science is the key to unlocking the potential of the plant-based category. #ad
